(6, 1, '2025-03-03 21:08:54', '2025-03-03 21:08:54', '<img width=\"968\" height=\"301\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/header-image-for-gli-website-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" />															\n					<h2>Are You a UM Student That Needs Help Finding Housing?<br></h2>				\n		<p>Take a quiz to figure out what student housing works for you based on your income, demographics, and preferences!</p><p> </p>		\n					<a href=\"#\">\n									Take the Quiz!\n					</a>\n		<p>This site was created for a GLI capstone project in 2025 to help understand the connection between housing and student well-being. Figuring out where to live for some of the most important years of our lives is extremely important, and we hope that this website can be a resource for new incoming students or for seasoned UM students that want to know about other options in their area.</p>', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2025-04-21 05:16:17', '2025-04-21 05:16:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/?page_id=6', 0, 'page', '', 0),
