(178, 1, '2025-04-21 02:48:26', '2025-04-21 02:48:26', '<img width=\"968\" height=\"301\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/header-image-for-gli-website-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" />															\n					<h2><h2 data-elementor-setting-key=\"title\" data-pen-placeholder=\"Type Here...\" style=\"font-size: 56px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 600;font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif;text-align: center\">Missoula Housing Options<br></h2></h2>				\n					<h2>On-Campus Dorms</h2>				\n					<h2>Aber Hall</h2>				\n		<p>Aber Hall is located on campus next to the recreation center and the University Center, it houses double rooms from floors 7-11.</p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); text-align: var(--text-align); font-size: 1rem;\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/aber/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/aber/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Craig Hall</h2>				\n		<p>Craig Hall is located on campus next to the Lodge as well as Elrod Hall and Duniway Hall, it has four stories and has double and triple rooms with single ADA compliant rooms as well. </p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"transition-property: all; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/craig/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/craig/default.php</a></p><p> </p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Duniway Hall</h2>				\n		<p>Duniway Hall is located on campus and connects Elrod and Craig. It has four stories with double rooms.</p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"transition-property: all; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/duniway/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/duniway/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Elrod Hall</h2>				\n		<p>Elrod Hall is located on campus next to Duniway and Craig, it\'s three stories tall and houses single, double, and triple rooms for male students.</p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"transition-property: all; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/elrod/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/elrod/default.php</a></p><p> </p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Jesse Hall</h2>				\n		<p>Jesse Hall is located on campus next to the Business Building, it has 11 stories and houses double rooms.</p>\n<p>Link to see more:&nbsp; &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/jesse/default.php\" style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/jesse/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img sr