ten minute walk north of campus near downtown Missoula. It houses studio, one bedroom, two bedroom, and four bedroom apartments.</p><p>Link to see more: <a style=\"font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); text-align: var(--text-align); font-size: 1rem;\" href=\"https://liveatroam.com/\">https://liveatroam.com/</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>The Sawyer Student Living</h2>				\n		<p>The Sawyer is west of campus and a 15 minute walk to downtown Missoula but campus is easily accessible by bus. It houses two bedroom, three bedroom and four bedroom apartments.</p><p>Link to see more: <a style=\"font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); text-align: var(--text-align); font-size: 1rem;\" href=\"https://www.sawyerliving.com/\">https://www.sawyerliving.com/</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />', 'Housing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-04-21 05:14:27', '2025-04-21 05:14:27', '', 25, 'http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/?p=182', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
