\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Knowles Hall</h2>				\n		<p>Knowles Hall is located on campus next to Turner and the Lodge, it houses double rooms with coed options.</p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/knowles/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/knowles/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Miller Hall</h2>				\n		<p>Miller Hall is located on campus next to the Panzer Hall, Duniway Hall, and the Lodge, it has 5 stories and houses double rooms, three person pods, and single rooms.</p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/miller/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/miller/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Panzer Hall</h2>				\n		<p>Panzer Hall is located on campus next Miller and Elrod Hall, it has 4 stories and houses four person suites (with two bathrooms) and single ADA-compliant rooms. </p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/panzer/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/panzer/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Turner Hall</h2>				\n		<p>Turner Hall is located on campus next to Knowles Hall, it has 3 stories and houses double rooms (with a sink) and single rooms for female students.</p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/turner/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/rh/descriptions/turner/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Off-Campus UM Housing</h2>				\n					<h2>Lewis and Clark Village</h2>				\n		<p>Lewis and Clark Village is located south of the main campus area, it\'s only a mile away from the main campus so its accessible by bus, foot, and bike. It houses three bedroom apartments and two bedroom apartments.</p><p>Link to see more: <a style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/lcv/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/lcv/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Craighead/Sisson Village</h2>				\n		<p>Craighead/Sisson Village are X-shaped buildings that are located south of the main campus area. It houses, studios, one bedroom, two bedroom, three bedroom apartments and four bedroom apartments.</p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/uv/descriptions/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/uv/descriptions/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Elliott Village</h2>				\n		<p>Elliott Village are two story buildings that are located south of the main campus area. It houses, studios, one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom apartments.</p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/uv/descriptions/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/uv/descriptions/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Toole Village</h2>				\n		<p>Elliott Village are two story buildings that are located south of the main campus area. It houses, studios, one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom apartments with ADA accessible options.</p><p>Link to see more:   <a style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\" href=\"https://www.umt.edu/housing/uv/descriptions/default.php\">https://www.umt.edu/housing/uv/descriptions/default.php</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>Off-Campus Non-UM Housing</h2>				\n					<h2>ROAM Student Living</h2>				\n		<p>ROAM is a ten minute walk north of campus near downtown Missoula. It houses studio, one bedroom, two bedroom, and four bedroom apartments.</p><p>Link to see more: <a style=\"font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); text-align: var(--text-align); font-size: 1rem;\" href=\"https://liveatroam.com/\">https://liveatroam.com/</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n					<h2>The Sawyer Student Living</h2>				\n		<p>The Sawyer is west of campus and a 15 minute walk to downtown Missoula but campus is easily accessible by bus. It houses two bedroom, three bedroom and four bedroom apartments.</p><p>Link to see more: <a style=\"font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight ); text-align: var(--text-align); font-size: 1rem;\" href=\"https://www.sawyerliving.com/\">https://www.sawyerliving.com/</a></p>		\n															<img src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/images/placeholder.png\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />', 'Housing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-04-21 05:15:45', '2025-04-21 05:15:45', '', 25, 'http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/?p=185', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(186, 1, '2025-04-21 05:16:17', '2025-04-21 05:16:17', '<img width=\"968\" height=\"301\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/header-image-for-gli-website-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" />															\n					<h2>Are You a UM Student That Needs Help Finding Housing?<br></h2>				\n		<p>Take a quiz to figure out what student housing works for you based on your income, demographics, and preferences!</p><p> </p>		\n					<a href=\"#\">\n									Take the Quiz!\n					</a>\n		<p>This site was created for a GLI capstone project in 2025 to help understand the connection between housing and student well-being. Figuring out where to live for some of the most important years of our lives is extremely important, and we hope that this website can be a resource for new incoming students or for seasoned UM students that want to know about other options in their area.</p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-04-21 05:16:17', '2025-04-21 05:16:17', '', 6, 'http://localhost/wordpressGLIstudentrec/?p=186', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
